          "reviewBody": "Rajasthan Vidya Mandir is one of the best schools in the city of Kolkata. The art of teaching is one of the exemplary facets that has elevated the standard of the school where it is today now. The education imparted to the students of the school hugely benefits the young minds to help them build their future. As a parent, I'm fully satisfied to have put my child in that school. It's a haven for budding talents that are nurtured to bloom to their fullest expanding their petals independently.",
