          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "One of the best school in Central Kolkata Locality. It not only focuses on the academic development of a student but also in the all round development. The school gives a lot of opportunities to it's  students to embrace themselves in various fields such as Dance, Drama, Singing, Debate, Creative Writing, Event Management and many more. I am proud to be a student of this Institution and I recommend it to all the parents who are searching for a perfect school for their children. An all girls atmosphere of the school keeps it calm and disciplined. They have the best faculty which consists of highly qualified and experienced teachers. They all are very kind and helpful.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
